            <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-tempo-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-8 bg-tempo-gold rounded-full inline-block"></span>ðŸ“š Tempo Prompt #1: áƒ™áƒšáƒ˜áƒ”áƒœáƒ¢áƒ˜áƒ¡ áƒ™áƒ˜áƒ—áƒ®áƒ•áƒáƒ–áƒ” áƒžáƒáƒ¡áƒ£áƒ®áƒ˜</h3>
